ntre building in the South Korean city of Jecheon, officials said, in one of the country's deadliest fire disasters. December 21, 2017 In "News" At least 18 people were killed and 24 injured Thursday in a major blaze at a building housing a sports centre and public bath in the South Korean city of Jecheon, officials said. December 21, 2017 In "News" At least 18 people were killed and 24 injured Thursday in a major blaze at a building housing a sports centre and public bath in the South Korean city of Jecheon, officials said. December 21, 2017 In "News"